{
  "stem": "24130.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Tell us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Is it true?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We already smell the smoke and the flesh.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we still didn't want to believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So there was this-- this gypsies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, they start giving-- they gave us coffee while we were on [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the gypsies came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They knew already that we would drink it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We would eat it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they came to take it from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So-- the-- this was a very tough thing to believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So when we came into the barracks, they gave us lunch, soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And each-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] and each cubby, they would get one plate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they says, where are the spoons?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They says, what spoons?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You drink from eat-- everybody takes a sip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I said, how could that be?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But you know, we were so hungry already, so thirsty, that we say, we better give in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We better start drinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we already ate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We drink that soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we were only three days in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After three days, they came again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't select us, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just counted a certain amount of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us back to a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this train wasn't so crowded anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they put about a hundred girls on one train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we went about three hours on that train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got to Krakau in Poland, a city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We saw the station's Krakau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got off this train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we walked to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We came there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before we came to this camp, it was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was on the cemetery from Krakau [INAUDIBLE] that-- that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And before we came, there were children in this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they took out two-- from two barracks, the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
